data.title: College Search Resources
data.meta_description: College Search Resources - Marquette University High School is an all-boys Catholic, Jesuit college prep high school in Milwaukee dedicated to faith, scholarship and community.
data.text:
These identified programs work with high school and college students in multiple capacities and provide academic, financial, social, and professional support to assistant historically underrepresented students to obtain a college education.
